{"tid":2022861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實用twitter根本唔洗人教 係你連ac都唔開咁解","createTime":"2020-05-18T14:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T13:54:49.000Z","uid":35562,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"781193745c5949cfc0ce89dcf57edae029a9383e","tid":2022861,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"見到好多ching係咁出post教人點玩twitter<br />\n呢度應該平均年齡都唔知有冇30歲 唔洗好似電腦班教阿婆咁教下話<br />\n基本上你自己開個ac禁下d hastag黎望下 睇下d名人(e.g G瘋)個AC下面D留言你都識用啦<br />\n根本咩唔識用都係藉口黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13c15b6fe27c1d9b851bbdac9a820ad3d776a4e","tid":2022861,"uid":35562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"同埋成班又驚唔識英文又盛<br />\n又唔見你用FACEBOOK咁多野驚<br />\n你就算真係廢到唔識打字都識rt下新聞加下hashtag啦<br />\n冇人follow你跟咪鳩follow人睇下有冇respond<br />\n打個tweet都要問問問你估做功課咩"},{"pid":"318954438ee73cc662315dee60fd2ea4a3abadc4","tid":2022861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"繼續努力"},{"pid":"0864afa266eba0f1602d2b9c644475cfe2176051","tid":2022861,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"自己做好自己<br />\n問心無愧就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好放棄<br />\n同時希望多D巴絲加入Twitter戰線"},{"pid":"7791c9123011d57bf81f5de85a27953b22b5c032","tid":2022861,"uid":204243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人開"},{"pid":"aedfdb72376efd9a4c8ac8f0e40673286afbd82c","tid":2022861,"uid":145446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人一齊加入twitter戰線<br />\n明明係最無成本嘅一條戰線，偏偏嚟嚟去去都係得嗰千幾二千人打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"5cabc659fd588ff17eaddf95d22b47b421eaa90c","tid":2022861,"uid":312885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"Twitter 上面有班小學雞成日屌人淨係rt 同hashtag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a22587743ecf8eed804784710498d545f91742","tid":2022861,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"淨係要你㩒幾個掣姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77905326a4d18b3518f44ed743f3442b80a52669","tid":2022861,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"Agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5375fd15b345bc32bf05e11a394e7a165cfbec","tid":2022861,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"TG一個group都幾萬人<br />\nTwitter搵5000活躍玩家睇下好嗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家諗下自己細個唔識日文 冇攻略咁爆pokemon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家話唔識用Twitter (有中文介面 有中文教學 仲有翻譯)<br />\n有冇覺得少少羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037fa14420721b85195b47944c9dfb8cecb30725","tid":2022861,"uid":244943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"要學嘅唔係點用，係點樣先可以合作推到post<br />\n例如:<br />\n* 應該推咩, follow手足再互推，定搵twitter help bot / act4hk<br />\n* 應該點推, tweet with comment vs 齋tweet, etc"},{"pid":"f6a98f9397ba04250ec7be451850f3ef16ada64e","tid":2022861,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037fa14420721b85195b47944c9dfb8cecb30725","tid":2022861,"uid":244943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"要學嘅唔係點用，係點樣先可以合作推到post<br />\n例如:<br />\n* 應該推咩, follow手足再互推，定搵twitter help bot / act4hk<br />\n* 應該點推, tweet with comment vs 齋tweet, etc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"Like &amp; retweet <br />\n除非多follower 如果唔係直接reply 原tweet係最好"},{"pid":"1319889dde78a4da379ffcbf9e87bae3b39d75c4","tid":2022861,"uid":237465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"我係有時唔明, 點解打打下字0既時候,  好似控制唔到個 KEYBOARD出字. <br />\n<br />\n另一方面還在研究緊 # &amp; @  ,<br />\n# 有時會見到某一堆野, 但有時又唔明點解冇左果個 HASHTAG  如 #HUWANVIRUS, 有時會有, 有時又唔知點解唔出現.<br />\n<br />\n誠言, 英文唔係細佬母語, 雖然有堆人讚細佬英文好, 入到場, 都要KEEP 住茶字典, 所以係 TWITTER 出現的時間不會太多.  幸好沒用 IG &amp; FB ( FB 係3年幾前已經放棄了 )"},{"pid":"c27fac5ca87385a0c90620a055e4a9e4685bf95c","tid":2022861,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cabc659fd588ff17eaddf95d22b47b421eaa90c","tid":2022861,"uid":312885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"Twitter 上面有班小學雞成日屌人淨係rt 同hashtag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"咁事實真係有班人玩下TWITTER都要學人扮大佬<br />\n好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a756cad63bae81f6ae5715fb56c350d7b95c56","tid":2022861,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e8c1d6305a345f356ff216ebf32c16dfcb6fb1","tid":2022861,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1319889dde78a4da379ffcbf9e87bae3b39d75c4","tid":2022861,"uid":237465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:02:45.000Z","msg":"我係有時唔明, 點解打打下字0既時候,  好似控制唔到個 KEYBOARD出字. <br />\n<br />\n另一方面還在研究緊 # &amp; @  ,<br />\n# 有時會見到某一堆野, 但有時又唔明點解冇左果個 HASHTAG  如 #HUWANVIRUS, 有時會有, 有時又唔知點解唔出現.<br />\n<br />\n誠言, 英文唔係細佬母語, 雖然有堆人讚細佬英文好, 入到場, 都要KEEP 住茶字典, 所以係 TWITTER 出現的時間不會太多.  幸好沒用 IG &amp; FB ( FB 係3年幾前已經放棄了 )"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"唔使理#出咩唔出咩，你Hashtag 嗰個term就當有"}